## How to Run

1. Clone this repository
2. Install required R packages: `install.packages(c("tidyverse", "fredr", "lmtest", "sandwich", "plm", "stargazer"))`
3. Set your FRED API key: `fredr_set_key("YOUR_API_KEY")` (obtain free at https://fred.stlouisfed.org/docs/api/api_key.html)
4. Run scripts in order: `01_data_collection.R` → `02_data_cleaning.R` → `03_eda.R` → `04_regression_analysis.R`

